# Python Projects Directory

Place your Python projects here.

Each project should be in its own subdirectory:

```
python/
├── project1/
│   ├── main.py
│   ├── requirements.txt
│   └── README.md
├── project2/
│   └── ...
└── ...
```

## Quick Start

Inside the container:

```bash
cd /workspace
python3 your_script.py
```

## Virtual Environments

For project-specific dependencies:

```bash
cd your_project/
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
